<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Quizer - About</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --bg: #ffffff; --card: #f4f4f6; --card-hover: #eaeaef;
      --border: rgba(0,0,0,0.08); --border-h: rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
      --text: #111114; --muted: #666672; --accent: #5a4ee8; --accent2: #1aaa88;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      :root {
        --bg: #1e1e22; --card: #313138; --card-hover: #3a3a44;
        --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); --border-h: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
        --text: #e8e8ec; --muted: #8a8a98; --accent: #7c6ff7; --accent2: #4fcfae;
      }
    }
    body {
      background: var(--bg); color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh; padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .page { width: 100%; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; animation: fadeUp 0.3s ease both; }

    /* topbar */
    .topbar { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; max-width:560px; margin-bottom: 2rem;}
    .back-btn { width:36px; height:36px; border-radius:10px; background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; text-decoration:none; transition:background 0.15s; flex-shrink:0; }
    .back-btn:hover { background:var(--card-hover); }
    .back-btn svg { width:18px; height:18px; stroke:var(--text); fill:none; stroke-width:2; stroke-linecap:round; stroke-linejoin:round; }
    .topbar-title { font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:700; }

    /* sections */
    .section {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    }
    .section p { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text); }
    .section p + p { margin-top: 0.5rem; }

    .feature-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .feature-list li {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }
    .feature-list li::before {
      content: '';
      width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600;
      background: rgba(90,78,232,0.12); color: var(--accent);
    }

    /* logo small */
    .logo-sm {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <div class="topbar">
  <a href="/home" class="back-btn">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/></svg>
  </a>
  <span class="topbar-title">About</span>
</div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Introduction</div>
    <p>This web app was made to help people post quizzes rapidly, and let other students attend, participate, and view their grades.</p>
    <p>Web app was made by students at <em>Cairo University</em>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Features</div>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>Create and publish quizzes instantly</li>
      <li>Search and join quizzes</li>
      <li>View your grades and history</li>
      <li>Secure login with Firebase</li>
      <li>Google Sign-in support</li>
      <li>Dark & Light mode</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">App Info</div>
    <p>App: <span class="logo-sm">Quizer</span></p>
    <p style="margin-top:6px">Version: <span class="badge">v1.0.0</span></p>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
